Package: textpress
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight and User-Friendly Natural Language Processing Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2023-11-21
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jason", "Timm", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides a suite of tools for basic natural language processing tasks. Designed to be lightweight and user-friendly, it includes functionalities for text tokenization, basic text analysis, and pattern searching within text corpora. It's particularly suitable for quick analyses and for users who prefer a simple toolkit for NLP tasks.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
